This assignment will be graded on a combination of functionality and style. A base grade will be determined from the general level of functionality of the program Does it read and write files successfully? Does it count correctly? Does it report the counts in the correct format? The base grade will be recorded as a mark out of 14.
Style will be marked on a subtractive scale from 0 to -3. For example, an assignment that receives a base mark of 12, but has several stylistic problems such as improper use of functions or insufficient comments resulting in a -2 adjustment will receive an overall mark of 10.
